WEBVTT

00:12:29.167 --> 00:12:30.625
we need to listen.

00:12:32.417 --> 00:12:35.143
Despite all this questioning --

00:12:35.167 --> 00:12:36.518
and there's a lot of it --

00:12:36.542 --> 00:12:39.833
I hear probably more
than a lot of people --

00:12:40.792 --> 00:12:42.309
I am an optimist.

00:12:42.333 --> 00:12:46.893
And my optimism
is with a younger generation.

00:12:46.917 --> 00:12:52.601
The younger generation
who actually now are becoming very aware

00:12:52.625 --> 00:12:54.934
of the risks of social media,

00:12:54.958 --> 00:12:56.726
the false news,

00:12:56.750 --> 00:12:58.500
the false identities,

00:12:59.708 --> 00:13:02.601
and they're starting to embrace science.